i\" />"},{"pid":"13111b6051b1223c1dae25af655e5ef5e6f6527e","tid":340153,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過個女仔同朋友傾計個陣笑得勁甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下完全比佢吸引住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過好多次<br />\n不過第二日就唔記得<br />\n盤唔算"},{"pid":"86aa4a1ee0f5c142397775b355d03557a31c22fc","tid":340153,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見過個女仔同朋友傾計個陣笑得勁甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下完全比佢吸引住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過好多次<br />\n不過第二日就唔記得<br />\n算唔算</blockquote>"},{"pid":"72b19c2b01c18e94bb5c98e668599b13659aaf07","tid":340153,"uid":54173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:47:38.000Z","msg":"中三去到新中學試過<br />\n不過毒撚唔敢同佢講野<br />\n點知去到中五佢倒追番我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住大學去Exchange <br />\nOrientation嗰陣係個lecture hall到見到個女仔 又係一見就好有feel<br />\n以為唔會有機會識<br />\n點知Friend搭friend咁認識左 好快就一齊左<br />\n但係都散左了"},{"pid":"f5307914e4ec658212a60fe666f86d7ad22cc0c2","tid":340153,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:15:52.000Z","msg":"有 係度見到樓主就鍾意咗樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5321a6a940afc6c679567154fd3e1cf19e5a5d0","tid":340153,"uid":9647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:00:51.000Z","msg":"成日都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37a61306830fc117471767cbe708d6a1129c90d","tid":340153,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:04:55.000Z",